node.text:
On the stunning east coast of Australia is this divine, private eco home - beautifully created, divinely inspired and perfectly peaceful -
surrounded by golden beaches, crystal clear oceans, pure, clean air, and untouched wilderness...
For more info visit www.forsalemilton.com 
Designed and built by @greendraft_design
Video by @gccvisuals

#nswsouthcoast #australia #designer #builder #dreamhome #architecturedaily #residentialdesign #style #beautifulinteriors #luxuryhomes

node.text:
Hugo Suissas is a self-taught #Lisbon-based #photographer who proves that you can make any photo much more interesting by trying out a different #perspective. He turns simple bridges and landscapes into surreal and fantastical places, and items like keys, fruits, and kids' toys into magical props. 

Every single #photograph has a different #story and a different #idea. They help us see the dull and boring #world that we're used to in a new and more fun way.
Via @fatstudios
-
#travel #design #photography #art

Andreas @Wannerstedt is a Stockholm based digital artist and art director who crafts unique 3D sculptures and mesmerizing looping animations.
The imagery of Andreas is both sophisticated and whimsical, and his synchronized animations has often been described as “oddly satisfying”, since the overall effect often evokes a strangely hypnotizing feeling.
Via @housesaddictive @housesgram
